name: Izumi-chan
description: Izumi: The origin story of Neiro When Neiro lived on the streets of Japan she was rescued by a that named her Izumi-chan. Afterwards, Izumi got adopted and eventually ended up with Kabosumama, who name her Neiro-chan. Izumi is the origin story of Neiro, the backstory of the favorite dog of this crypto cycle! ZUMI is a CTO with strong foundations on Transparency, communication and positioning our community on a player vs engine (PvE) scenario by the blow-off top of the Bull Run.
